    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>Holding a small silver mirror, you catch the reflection of your chosen target. A shimmering barrier forms around the target. This barrier doesn't physically block attacks, but it make it difficult for creatures to mentally focus on directly attacking the shielded target.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong> </p><ul><li><p>You ward a creature within range against attack. Until the spell ends, any creature who decides to target the warded creature with an attack or a spell or ability that does damage must first make a wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature must choose a new target. A creature rolls this save before moving to the shielded creature, if applicable, and can move after failing the save to reach a new target.</p></li><li><p>If the warded creature makes an attack, casts a spell that affects an enemy, or deals damage to another creature, this spell ends.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>A target affected by Sanctuary can be targeted by area of effect abilities that deal damage without the user first rolling a wisdom saving throw, but only if the target of Sanctuary is not the only target of the ability.</em></p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Buff</strong> </p><ul><li><p>You ward a creature within range against attack. Until the spell ends, any creature who decides to target the warded creature with an attack or a spell or ability that does damage must first make a wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature must choose a new target. A creature rolls this save before moving to the shielded creature, if applicable, and can move after failing the save to reach a new target.</p></li><li><p>If the warded creature makes an attack, casts a spell that affects an enemy, or deals damage to another creature, this spell ends.</p></li></ul><p></p>"
        },
